room_title: Escape room "Exodus" by Escape Room Madness in New York
room_address: 38 W. 32nd St, Ste 606 New York, NY 10001
room_description: Something has gone wrong at the New York History Museum. The ghost of the evil Pharaoh Ramses II has possessed the curator and set in motion events that could end the world. Can you and your team, with the help of the good Pharaoh Khufu, save humanity?
